__NAME__ purpose
display prices with tax amount included
__END__

__NAME__ see also
__END__

__NAME__ notes
For a complete introduction to taxes, please see the 
&glos-tax; glossary entry.
__END__

__NAME__ synopsis
<group choice='plain'>
	<arg choice='plain'>No</arg>
	<arg choice='plain'>Yes</arg>
</group>
__END__


__NAME__ description
Display product &glos-price;s with &glos-tax; amount included
(instead of calculating and displaying tax amount separately).
This is common in European countries.
__END__

__NAME__ example: Enabling TaxInclusive
<programlisting>
TaxInclusive 1
</programlisting>
__END__

__NAME__ author
&racke;
__END__
